{"tid":2414211,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"可唔可以唔用微積分解呢條行程問題","createTime":"2021-02-19T08:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T12:10:35.000Z","uid":359621,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"9fc82090c4527fb393e1e12037576544f5688683","tid":2414211,"uid":359621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T08:43:56.000Z","msg":"可能大家讀小學見過以下既行程問題<br />\n假設甲喺乙以北一公里 佢哋同時以均勻速度相向而行 甲既速度係乙既兩倍 好容易計倒當甲行左2/3公里（乙行左1/3公里）佢哋就相遇<br />\n如果佢哋同時以如上既速度向南行 咁樣亦都可以容易計倒當甲行左2公里（乙行左1公里）甲就追到乙<br />\n以上兩條問題 甲同乙都係喺同一條線上面行 依家我地不妨考慮一個複雜小小既情況<br />\n假設佢哋同一時間出發 同之前一樣 以均勻速度行 甲既速度係乙既兩倍 乙向東行 而甲就追住乙咁行（即係甲既速度向量（velocity vector）總係指向乙）咁乙行幾遠就被甲追倒？<br />\n我知道答案 數字幾靚 但係想知可唔可以唔用微積分計倒呢？最好有一個小學生可以理解既解法"},{"pid":"f5f9ef27d8923cfcf58e5488dbd6e833e0f3542d","tid":2414211,"uid":272968,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:51:31.000Z","msg":"咪即係搵兩條linear equation嘅相交點"},{"pid":"c42bec110f68f3160fae1cf7865626b1691f0ddc","tid":2414211,"uid":272968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5f9ef27d8923cfcf58e5488dbd6e833e0f3542d","tid":2414211,"uid":272968,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:51:31.000Z","msg":"咪即係搵兩條linear equation嘅相交點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:52:41.000Z","msg":"前提係方向恆定 一變條route就變左曲線 成條數麻煩好多"},{"pid":"4c5f56a85bd2aa351581ca78c95f607118964120","tid":2414211,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:53:36.000Z","msg":"呢呢問題係relative speed問題, 唔需要用微積分<br />\n<br />\n車速有變化先需要用微分"},{"pid":"5b931670a0149560a46410c53c5b56d605cdfef2","tid":2414211,"uid":367224,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4c5f56a85bd2aa351581ca78c95f607118964120","tid":2414211,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:53:36.000Z","msg":"呢呢問題係relative speed問題, 唔需要用微積分<br />\n<br />\n車速有變化先需要用微分"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:55:29.000Z","msg":"甲喺乙以北 乙向東行 甲向乙行 點睇都係曲線<br />\n點會冇變化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df4ac969b55571ad434bb433dcc1c9d1830a6b73","tid":2414211,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b931670a0149560a46410c53c5b56d605cdfef2","tid":2414211,"uid":367224,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4c5f56a85bd2aa351581ca78c95f607118964120","tid":2414211,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:53:36.000Z","msg":"呢呢問題係relative speed問題, 唔需要用微積分<br />\n<br />\n車速有變化先需要用微分"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:55:29.000Z","msg":"甲喺乙以北 乙向東行 甲向乙行 點睇都係曲線<br />\n點會冇變化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:58:04.000Z","msg":"兩者定速行個relative speed都係不變<br />\n<br />\n呢個係galilean transformation, 結果係A睇B行進方向速度同第三者睇唔同, 但都係constant velocity<br />\n<br />\nv_resultant = v_a-v_b, 除返t = 0個distance就得"},{"pid":"3022f4f7a3a56b0023e0a10c8f1f8602a9cea48e","tid":2414211,"uid":107469,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:59:09.000Z","msg":"Let S be distance traveled in time t by B<br />\nvelocity of B = v; A = 2v<br />\ndistance traveled by A: S+1=2vt <br />\ndistance traveled by B: S=vt<br />\nSolving the Eqn, S=1km<br />\n唔洗用calculus其實"},{"pid":"f02f64e905f3e3b2454a8d0c62c1a4ba03dcaa37","tid":2414211,"uid":367224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df4ac969b55571ad434bb433dcc1c9d1830a6b73","tid":2414211,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b931670a0149560a46410c53c5b56d605cdfef2","tid":2414211,"uid":367224,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4c5f56a85bd2aa351581ca78c95f607118964120","tid":2414211,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:53:36.000Z","msg":"呢呢問題係relative speed問題, 唔需要用微積分<br />\n<br />\n車速有變化先需要用微分"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:55:29.000Z","ms