re":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f02f64e905f3e3b2454a8d0c62c1a4ba03dcaa37","tid":2414211,"uid":367224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df4ac969b55571ad434bb433dcc1c9d1830a6b73","tid":2414211,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b931670a0149560a46410c53c5b56d605cdfef2","tid":2414211,"uid":367224,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:55:29.000Z","msg":"甲喺乙以北 乙向東行 甲向乙行 點睇都係曲線<br />\n點會冇變化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:58:04.000Z","msg":"兩者定速行個relative speed都係不變<br />\n<br />\n呢個係galilean transformation, 結果係A睇B行進方向速度同第三者睇唔同, 但都係constant velocity<br />\n<br />\nv_resultant = v_a-v_b, 除返t = 0個distance就得"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:01:02.000Z","msg":"而家冇change in speed但有change in direction <br />\n甲喺個accelerating frame入面"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:16:05.000Z","msg":"無睇到個轉向問題, 成件事即刻唔同計法<br />\n<br />\n呢個情況會有3個solution:<br />\n<br />\n1. a未到橫行就掂到b<br />\n2. a岩岩開始南vector = 0 就掂到b<br />\n3. a去到b既尾, 南向量變0再跟住只有東向量追上B<br />\n<br />\n2可以reduce做1既special case, 要拆開2個唔同情況計"},{"pid":"e305b72bfc292845198a73f47f9b2522e9a53060","tid":2414211,"uid":367224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e2e493e8f5a3fe42a6b5430b65de75b8dba505e","tid":2414211,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f02f64e905f3e3b2454a8d0c62c1a4ba03dcaa37","tid":2414211,"uid":367224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df4ac969b55571ad434bb433dcc1c9d1830a6b73","tid":2414211,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:58:04.000Z","msg":"兩者定速行個relative speed都係不變<br />\n<br />\n呢個係galilean transformation, 結果係A睇B行進方向速度同第三者睇唔同, 但都係constant velocity<br />\n<br />\nv_resultant = v_a-v_b, 除返t = 0個distance就得"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:01:02.000Z","msg":"而家冇change in speed但有change in direction <br />\n甲喺個accelerating frame入面"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:16:05.000Z","msg":"無睇到個轉向問題, 成件事即刻唔同計法<br />\n<br />\n呢個情況會有3個solution:<br />\n<br />\n1. a未到橫行就掂到b<br />\n2. a岩岩開始南vector = 0 就掂到b<br />\n3. a去到b既尾, 南向量變0再跟住只有東向量追上B<br />\n<br />\n2可以reduce做1既special case, 要拆開2個唔同情況計"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:18:12.000Z","msg":"樓主應該想唔用calculus解釋3<br />\n我諗唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d1c4d159f36f6d9822100ec6566dde850895bc4","tid":2414211,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e2e493e8f5a3fe42a6b5430b65de75b8dba505e","tid":2414211,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f02f64e905f3e3b2454a8d0c62c1a4ba03dcaa37","tid":2414211,"uid":367224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df4ac969b55571ad434bb433dcc1c9d1830a6b73","tid":2414211,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:58:04.000Z","msg":"兩者定速行個relative speed都係不變<br />\n<br />\n呢個係galilean transformation, 結果係A睇B行進方向速度同第三者睇唔同, 但都係constant velocity<br />\n<br />\nv_resultant = v_a-v_b, 除返t = 0個distance就得"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:01:02.000Z","msg":"而家冇change in speed但有change in direction <br />\n甲喺個accelerating frame入面"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:16:05.000Z","msg":"無睇到個轉向問題, 成件事即刻唔同計法<br />\n<br />\n呢個情況會有3個solution:<br />\n<br />\n1. a未到橫行就掂到b<br />\n2. a岩岩開始南vector = 0 就掂到b<br />\n3. a去到b既尾, 南向量變0再跟住只有東向量追上B<br />\n<br />\n2可以reduce做1既special case, 要拆開2個唔同情況計"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:20:13.000Z","msg":"Va = a1 i + a2 j <br />\nVb = b1 i <br />\nVa^2 = a1^2 + a2^2<br />\n<br />\nVab = Va - Vb = (a1 - b1)i + a2 j = (a1 - Vb)i + sqrt(Va^2 - a1^2) j<br />\n<br />\n再用唔同既情況sub返i j 方向同時性求解"},{"pid":"4b7b5e76a74be3022bb044e9d5ace3ba14df487a","tid":2414211,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e305b72bfc292845198a73f47f9b2522e9a53060","tid":2414211,"uid":367224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e2e493e8f5a3fe42a6b5430