rl=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FRadiodrome&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGoT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=a514f87e\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Radiodrome</a><br />\n啱啱上維基見到個解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"401d62fbbf6c924825e55a816985b70e5c248ebe","tid":2414211,"uid":141268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:42:07.000Z","msg":"腦諗會唔會係條橢圓曲線"},{"pid":"00f7b2bcb7da3a14715d796917abb5a455e40574","tid":2414211,"uid":359621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5eabd85e19ce98387e88de32747a12c28cb27ada","tid":2414211,"uid":66994,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T11:28:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Radiodrome\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FRadiodrome&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGoT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=a514f87e\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Radiodrome</a><br />\n啱啱上維基見到個解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:20:33.000Z","msg":"其實呢個問題係經典既運動學問題，有讀過year 1既classical mechanics或者以前既A level applied maths都應該識得用polar coordinates黎表示relative velocity vector從而（巧妙地）解一條ode既標準解法 。呢個解法比wiki嗰個仲短。亦都可以將原本既問題轉化成以下既幾何問題：假設x-axis指向東，y-axis指向北，咁甲可以假設喺(0, 1)嗰點，乙喺原點。搵一條喺(0, 1)開始既curve，使得上面任何一點同(0, 1)之間既arclength，總係嗰一點既tangent line既x-intercept既兩倍。咁樣可以set up 兩條ode黎solve呢條curve既x同y-coordinate。呢條curve其實可以用好簡單既polynomials黎parametrize，我好驚訝wiki比左咁核特既parametrization。據我所知，呢個polynomial parametrization喺現今既literature無出現過。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得呢條問題有唔需要微積分既解法係有原因，同我一開始提出既小學行程問題有關。等我遲d post我既見解。"},{"pid":"e797e5da26a963db262c51d56b1b4ba2ce441010","tid":2414211,"uid":359621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"401d62fbbf6c924825e55a816985b70e5c248ebe","tid":2414211,"uid":141268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:42:07.000Z","msg":"腦諗會唔會係條橢圓曲線"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:32:35.000Z","msg":"係 我計到既polynomial parametrization, x-coordinate係cubic polynomial，y-coordinate係quadratic polynomial，符合algebraic geometry既elliptic curve既定義<br />\n好好奇點解你會唸倒係elliptic curve"},{"pid":"948ddb39894e4d808aa6890cbe3982f43573ab36","tid":2414211,"uid":141268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e797e5da26a963db262c51d56b1b4ba2ce441010","tid":2414211,"uid":359621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"401d62fbbf6c924825e55a816985b70e5c248ebe","tid":2414211,"uid":141268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T12:42:07.000Z","msg":"腦諗會唔會係條橢圓曲線"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:32:35.000Z","msg":"係 我計到既polynomial parametrization, x-coordinate係cubic polynomial，y-coordinate係quadratic polynomial，符合algebraic geometry既elliptic curve既定義<br />\n好好奇點解你會唸倒係elliptic curve"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:43:55.000Z","msg":"天才呢家野。。。。"},{"pid":"cef26de48b893b74be3feb36fd995488eec5716f","tid":2414211,"uid":69866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:54:37.000Z","msg":"我入到<br />\n圖又冇"},{"pid":"c7228d613c66ea5350f10d219e378b2ef43fef4a","tid":2414211,"uid":279321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3022f4f7a3a56b0023e0a10c8f1f8602a9cea48e","tid":2414211,"uid":107469,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T09:59:09.000Z","msg":"Let S be distance traveled in time t by B<br />\nvelocity of B = v; A = 2v<br />\ndistance traveled by A: S+1=2vt <br />\ndistance traveled by B: S=vt<br />\nSolving the Eqn, S=1km<br />\n唔洗用calculus其實"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T14:00:59.000Z","msg":"S+1邊度嚟? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3de8fe6264295c2de4d6c157f774fdde4f42ff1b","tid":2414211,"uid":107469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":