7:09.000Z","msg":"個solution係錯既"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T02:50:47.000Z","msg":"咁個ans係咩？<br />\n我計到sqrt(1/3) 但係應該小學生唔會計到"},{"pid":"409281b0b8f00d93d2e3b33a46a2bf629c9848a2","tid":2414211,"uid":107469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ff34614441ca9b89a6b6e010359301ccee8d236","tid":2414211,"uid":107469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a1c10a1047d0e882dff2e31997519f386bebc5b","tid":2414211,"uid":359621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ecc6eb49ddedc5c39590d52cb3a1ae0a4bd0372","tid":2414211,"uid":107469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T14:21:43.000Z","msg":"Oh 冇野了 我睇錯以為2個向下行"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T15:17:09.000Z","msg":"個solution係錯既"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T02:50:47.000Z","msg":"咁個ans係咩？<br />\n我計到sqrt(1/3) 但係應該小學生唔會計到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T02:57:53.000Z","msg":"收返sor"},{"pid":"9de664f87fd3b7fc00a185a3dd05e0de04af29d8","tid":2414211,"uid":272677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fc82090c4527fb393e1e12037576544f5688683","tid":2414211,"uid":359621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T08:43:56.000Z","msg":"可能大家讀小學見過以下既行程問題<br />\n假設甲喺乙以北一公里 佢哋同時以均勻速度相向而行 甲既速度係乙既兩倍 好容易計倒當甲行左2/3公里（乙行左1/3公里）佢哋就相遇<br />\n如果佢哋同時以如上既速度向南行 咁樣亦都可以容易計倒當甲行左2公里（乙行左1公里）甲就追到乙<br />\n以上兩條問題 甲同乙都係喺同一條線上面行 依家我地不妨考慮一個複雜小小既情況<br />\n假設佢哋同一時間出發 同之前一樣 以均勻速度行 甲既速度係乙既兩倍 乙向東行 而甲就追住乙咁行（即係甲既速度向量（velocity vector）總係指向乙）咁乙行幾遠就被甲追倒？<br />\n我知道答案 數字幾靚 但係想知可唔可以唔用微積分計倒呢？最好有一個小學生可以理解既解法"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T03:38:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用微積分出個小學生都理解到嘅方法，呢個先係難度喎！定你想講起個模型出嚟俾你 visualise 佢？"},{"pid":"4b634b3cf557d56439d6059ec167f6e8d7b5ae8a","tid":2414211,"uid":272677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9de664f87fd3b7fc00a185a3dd05e0de04af29d8","tid":2414211,"uid":272677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fc82090c4527fb393e1e12037576544f5688683","tid":2414211,"uid":359621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T08:43:56.000Z","msg":"可能大家讀小學見過以下既行程問題<br />\n假設甲喺乙以北一公里 佢哋同時以均勻速度相向而行 甲既速度係乙既兩倍 好容易計倒當甲行左2/3公里（乙行左1/3公里）佢哋就相遇<br />\n如果佢哋同時以如上既速度向南行 咁樣亦都可以容易計倒當甲行左2公里（乙行左1公里）甲就追到乙<br />\n以上兩條問題 甲同乙都係喺同一條線上面行 依家我地不妨考慮一個複雜小小既情況<br />\n假設佢哋同一時間出發 同之前一樣 以均勻速度行 甲既速度係乙既兩倍 乙向東行 而甲就追住乙咁行（即係甲既速度向量（velocity vector）總係指向乙）咁乙行幾遠就被甲追倒？<br />\n我知道答案 數字幾靚 但係想知可唔可以唔用微積分計倒呢？最好有一個小學生可以理解既解法"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T03:38:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用微積分出個小學生都理解到嘅方法，呢個先係難度喎！定你想講起個模型出嚟俾你 visualise 佢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T03:42:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我自己視障，對唔住<br />\n轉頭同你諗下"},{"pid":"09d611da1da68af492c30a0c735b0a0e21898af4","tid":2414211,"uid":335003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T03:44:40.000Z","msg":"而家小學生要識 vector 咁開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d8ddd718115f2b3c920f54ff80ee462839bc05e","tid":2414211,"uid":179121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T03:48:37.000Z","msg":"列表解釋，port graphics <br />\n<br />\n甲乙的 時間距離關係"},{"pid":"28992b7218465a3f68b99ec606efc86c3221ef7c","tid":2414211,"uid":69866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T04:36:39.000Z","msg":"你有change of direction咪姐係有change of vector<br />\n<br />\n你拆返做x y , 兩個direction都唔係uniform speed<br />\ndAx= 2v cos Q<br />\ndAy=2v sin Q<br />\ndBx=v<br />\ndBy =0"},{"pid":"c36490995a312c84fcd46af5674a47b49f67fcb6","tid":2414211,"uid":69866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T04:38:14.000Z","msg":"calculus簡化左先有linear equation<br />\n唔好發夢，咩小學生都識唔洗calculus"},{"pid":"f6605fe61a787405e9a8bca68236ef523f038b30","tid":2414211,"uid":69866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T04:39:23.000Z","msg":"你真係要小學生學，<br />\n你用graph逐個time segment畫咪得"},{"pid":"9533ece9fb2249a8101c5d00414a838c24dd9937","tid":2414211,"uid":75193,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T05:00:13.000Z","msg":"其實會唔會太複雜 <br />\na想追到b<br />\n<br />\n當x係向東 <br />\nb車速度1 a車2<br />\na車想追到b車又唔會浪費時間應該係<br />\n大家x速度一樣 =1 <br />\n咁X^2+y^2=4 y=&radic;3 應該就計完<br />\n小學應該係咁上下啦 點會教佢諗一路彎住追"},{"pid":"3b54309195da785f3d824cbdc3d2d208aa8938b1","tid":2414211,"uid":359621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d8ddd718115f2b3c920f54ff80ee462839bc05e","tid":2414211,"uid":179121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T03:48:37.000Z","msg":"列表解釋，port graphics <br />\n<br />\n甲乙的 時間距離關係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T05:13:34.000Z","msg":"答案係一個分數 <br />\n<br />\n向小學生解釋 plot graph都算係一個選擇，可以先喺x-axis由0開始plot d 既倍數既點，即係(kd, 0), k係非負整數 (d係一個好細既數 例如0.01) 跟住用以下方法approximately plot 甲既路線。 由(0, 1)開始，畫一條指向(d, 0)既直線，跟住plot係(0, 1)同(d, 0)之間既線段，同(0, 1)距離係2d既點，叫呢點做A_1。Inductively，plot 左A_n之後，搵喺A_n同((n+1)d, 0)之間既線段，同A_n距離2d既點，叫呢點做A_(n+1)。將A_i呢啲點用線段連埋，就得到甲既近似路線。<br />\n<br />\n不過我想搵既solution，係可以準確地比倒乙要行左幾遠先比甲追到。"},{"pid":"f31c2b0cc883473011e1ae8a498cdb04d44f2a67","tid":2414211,"uid":379900,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T05:26:37.000Z","msg":"衝入黎答班友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再次見識到連登仔個種奇低既理解能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"322486a92f74e82f037bc9a3c50bf5aef04deeed","tid":2414211,"uid":359621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f31c2b0cc883473011e1ae8a498cdb04d44f2a67","tid":2414211,"uid":379900,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T05:26:37.000Z","msg":"衝入黎答班友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再次見識到連登仔個種奇低既理解能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T05:39:45.000Z","msg":"咁我問呢條問題，特登leng去兩條小學問題，搞到好多人以為條問題好簡單，係有少少misleading既。不過透過一問一答back and forth咁樣clarify，等多啲人問題難喺邊，都未嘗唔係一件好事黎既。"},{"pid":"bde9755cea8547ad6ceea871ffaabd578152d161","tid":2414211,"uid":359621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cef26de48b893b74be3feb36fd995488eec5716f","tid":2414211,"uid":69866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T13:54:37.000Z","msg":"我入到<br />\n圖又冇"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T06:55:20.000Z","msg":"之前有人post左條wiki link，嗰度可以搵倒圖。或者可以參考呢個link<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pursuit_curve\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FPursuit_curve&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGoT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=3c471a89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pursuit_curve</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ew6gLUu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEw6gLUu.png&h=f0b6333a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n都係嗰句啦，我好奇怪無人(wiki都無)指出甲既路線其實係一條algebraic curve。"},{"pid":"cdd09de4090ff31be02c98541f90cd8a19c463ae","tid":2414211,"uid":374198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T11:40:06.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪因為覺得第三條答案同第一二條嘅答案有某種對稱性，所以有方法唔洗用微積分。"},{"pid":"bd1b9f60f8a094375d8c508a3f8beb9b0e7d41af","tid":2414211,"uid":374198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T11:47:21.000Z","msg":"btw 條問題好有趣，thx。唔知點解有負評。"},{"pid":"6d9859f553d8a2c8efb0c93cb9a6ee2dc01c70c5","tid":2414211,"uid":359621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdd09de4090ff31be02c98541f90cd8a19c463ae","tid":2414211,"uid":374198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T11:40:06.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪因為覺得第三條答案同第一二條嘅答案有某種對稱性，所以有方法唔洗用微積分。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T12:36:40.000Z","msg":"Exactly! 三條問題嘅答案係有某種對稱性，同乙走嘅方向有關。除此之外，我覺得呢條問題可以唔使微積分解，亦都因為一條類似但更加經典嘅運動學問題，一開始係用好深嘅微積分搵答案，但係其實有一個衹用中學幾何學同物理嘅解法。<br />\n<br />\n我都唔知點解呢個post會有腐皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddeeeda45d2a7309f94d30fc50d4ff797eb229f5","tid":2414211,"uid":81788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T17:08:29.000Z","msg":"呢條問題幾有趣，留名先<br />\n我用咗個general approach去嘗試解，甲同乙嘅速度會出現喺某啲數嘅指數(乜乜乜嘅n次方)，會唔會因為甲乙嘅速度比咁啱係2，先會出到一個咁靚嘅數字？"},{"pid":"035c461c6c0e0d0f8677811d5b1553e7b0a67fce","tid":2414211,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f31c2b0cc883473011e1ae8a498cdb04d44f2a67","tid":2414211,"uid":379900,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T05:26:37.000Z","msg":"衝入黎答班友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再次見識到連登仔個種奇低既理解能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T17:30:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你就係其中一個"}]}